overview.en: AOM is an important component of DFBTC's cross-chain revenue, which is generated by the technology to solve the zero-interest assets of Bitcoin. DFBTC anchors BTC in the ETH network through cross-chain anchoring technology, providing higher liquidity. In the future, AOM will create more ways to generate income from high-quality assets, and in the later stage, it will cross-chain to other high-quality main chains to provide greater value.
overview.zh: AOM是DFBTC跨链的一个重要收益组成，通过技术解决比特币的零息资产而产生的，DFBTC通过跨链锚定技术锚定BTC在ETH网络，提供更高的流动性。AOM未来将打造更多的优质资产收益方式，后期将会跨链到其他优质主链提供增加更大价值。
